24T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"若是像我般戀上別個還想你會抱著我可不可<br />\n前度再好都要割斷再成為記念"},{"pid":"c9d2ca819b3d099844078161b6e38764d1ea297f","tid":2416973,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"回頭看最初多快樂 記得嗎"},{"pid":"0fca42dfa6af6d19faa9a3f9af868f33895085af","tid":2416973,"uid":25073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"喺香港地 為何多一個你"},{"pid":"315690914e872d8c79b48e80536dd274dda833be","tid":2416973,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"給我一首歌的時間"},{"pid":"28623ad15c674328d33c9593f9c2de02abe439e3","tid":2416973,"uid":200843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"而既然分開了　何必又想打擾<br />\n為何愛人丟低了　才來明白對方緊要<br />\n而既然分開了　問好亦不必要<br />\n原來我仍想知你　與情人近況<br />\n可會對我懷緬<br />\n<br />\n24-2-2021"},{"pid":"31b1d09f153a2e0f5d3b9ded3cc6f01b472b933c","tid":2416973,"uid":153459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"24/02/2021<br />\n<br />\n今天看這段歷史　像褪色午夜殘片 <br />\n笑話情節　此刻變窩心故事 <br />\n現時大了　那種心跳難重演 <br />\n極燦爛時光一去難再遇上一次"},{"pid":"bbfd882ddd534c5ef7b2710f277364d716be1f7e","tid":2416973,"uid":255036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:19:24.000Z","msg":"愛情好像流沙 我不掙扎 隨它去吧 我不害怕<br />\n愛情好像流沙 心裡的牽掛<br />\n不願放下 OH BABY 讓我這樣吧<br />\n<br />\n24/2/2021"},{"pid":"45be2762005344f3c88afed6f38fea2c6cbe84d5","tid":2416973,"uid":21282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"現實裡裝英勇難避免<br />\n成為了不懂哭也不想笑的一個漢子"},{"pid":"00e96330a53cc1f08e5cc713a7cc28f2727e88c2","tid":2416973,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"然後每一天 活得好你一點<br />\n來讓你今天碰見 那日離棄我 原是你損失<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e143e30d8daf369fd049f92ad86b2ab95a9e36d1","tid":2416973,"uid":57759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"長命先可以撐過去"},{"pid":"848327f43ae042a78f7a36181c05dfafaa0a51e7","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:07:06.000Z","msg":"24/02/21-每當變幻時<br />\n懷緬過去常陶醉 <br />\n一半樂事　一半令人流淚 <br />\n夢如人生　快樂永記取 <br />\n悲苦深刻藏骨髓 <br />\n<br />\n雖然首歌好舊，但幾好聽嘅<br />\n球場開翻一段時間，今日心血來潮自己一個去球場踢波。<br />\n諗翻起之前中學同班隊友著住件校隊波衫係球場榮辱共享嘅日子。<br />\n發現人就係咁，所有野都係失去左先識想念,珍惜<br />\n好掛住曾經義無反顧去愛我嘅你<br />\n好掛住著住校服無憂無慮嘅日子<br />\n好掛住以住無病無痛健康嘅身體"},{"pid":"a0246f5943bb41c8ac934b2def4f686922b895bb","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbd564fb5ddbf190784ec26fb4ecffac9448dc81","tid":2416973,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"若是像我般戀上別個還想你會抱著我可不可<br />\n前度再好都要割斷再成為記念"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"曾經最深愛嘅人，無論過幾耐都唔會忘記。<br />\n用殘忍嘅方法，去令我上一課，<br />\n佢嘅離開，點都會令我地成長。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a78cfb45dec15da0611801b1cb5dfc190861974","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9d2ca819b3d099844078161b6e38764d1ea297f","tid":2416973,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"回頭看最初多快樂 記得嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"點都會記得<br />\n但大局已定，已成過去<br />\n只可以閑時拎翻岀黎回昧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d79655aa25107c0e6c67486dabb0f4e4b2756c","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0fca42dfa6af6d19faa9a3f9af868f33895085af","tid":2416973,"uid":25073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"喺香港地 為何多一個你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:13:35.000Z","msg":"住係香港地　我愛香港地"},{"pid