673533d0043a5aec0f8fb3c3f37b28671bd016","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"25/02/21-百年樹人<br />\n在最燦爛時光交織美麗的錯愛 <br />\n若有無奈 只有用新的愛情來做替代 若看不開 <br />\n只不過從此沒有這麼緊張一段愛 未曾捉緊你那樣放開<br />\n<br />\n在我最無力為力，最唔成熟，最一事無成嘅時候<br />\n遇到一個我想照顧一世嘅女仔<br />\n當我成熟左啲，有翻啲能力嘅時候<br />\n呢個女仔已經離開左我<br />\n我仲好想照顧你，但我已經唔可以<br />\n希望你會再遇到一個好似我咁想照顧你一世嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5e6c51e8a5ec534c1e045b80d528ed4bf22ce2","tid":2416973,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439325519d321a3b61ffb3a11727b0a86c7df56f","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70537d6f28fa07dd5b588fa5d4b5077cc9f3a18b","tid":2416973,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78de8256e49c05e5c3e5f4273be814b153dcf011","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"比起我，更想你活得更好<br />\n更想宜加陪緊你嘅比我更好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"唔會 我相信自己係最好嘅 係佢走寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"希望你會令到佢後悔<br />\n加油巴打💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"唔想佢後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢會知道+接受我嘅好"},{"pid":"83fa4def0220f149bda95ffa70c9a168d14ab807","tid":2416973,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94db855b99882d795cb18b12865c77e995103ab","tid":2416973,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c820643f1cca3bb4f47a5b2e443f8ac21ab6129d","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n有時諗點先可以覆得更好<br />\n有時唔得閑<br />\n所以隔咗幾耐先覆到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我應承大家我每一個留言都會覆<br />\n歡迎大家一齊每日上黎放底段歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1763bd32d2238d9a3414e052a60f13be2b40f4c3","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b94db855b99882d795cb18b12865c77e995103ab","tid":2416973,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c820643f1cca3bb4f47a5b2e443f8ac21ab6129d","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n有時諗點先可以覆得更好<br />\n有時唔得閑<br />\n所以隔咗幾耐先覆到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我應承大家我每一個留言都會覆<br />\n歡迎大家一齊每日上黎放底段歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"我多謝你哋就真<br />\n有你哋嘅留言我得閒冇嘢做先有一啲野解下悶<br />\n不過都希望嚟緊會有更多人喺呢度每日留言<br />\n不過我私心希望正評快啲多翻過負評"},{"pid":"be8c55ae8ffb8b69b40fb2364baede890cc02fbe","tid":2416973,"uid":122231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"點樣死　點樣生存　莫非話我無撚用"},{"pid":"193b9ecf675c3647fc5ae1e96e644c2cb9278f99","tid":2416973,"uid":384124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83fa4def0220f149bda95ffa70c9a168d14ab807","tid":2416973,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"走了嗎 你想走